CVE.summary: Multiple SQL injection vulnerabilities in Wallpaper Website (Wallpaper Complete Website) 1.0.09 and earlier allow remote attackers to execute arbitrary SQL commands via the (1) login or (2) password parameter to (a) process.php, or the (3) wallpaperid parameter to (b) dlwallpaper.php.
